text: Vasile Moldovan (born 28 August 1911, date of death unknown) was a Romanian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1911 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Romanian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Romania Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Cluj- Napoca
